These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  project-manager, librarian, police-officer, chef, accountant, electrician
There are 6 different nationalities: canadian, japanese, egyptian, dutch, german, brazilian
1. the chef is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the japanese is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the project-manager is on the left of the librarian##1
4. the german is between the electrician and the canadian##2
5. the dutch is between the german and the japanese##2
6. the canadian is the chef##1
7. the accountant is on the left of the canadian##1
8. the brazilian is on the left of the librarian##1
9. the accountant is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Job           | project-manager | librarian | electrician | accountant | chef    | police-officer  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | japanese   | dutch       | german        | canadian | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: american, french, nigerian, spanish, russian, japanese
6 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, hedgehog, fish, cat, goldfish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the russian##1
3. the owner of the fish is between the spanish and the american##2
4. the nigerian is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the american is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the spanish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
8. the french is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Nationality   | french | japanese | russian | spanish | nigerian | american  |
| Pet           | goldfish | cat  | bird | ferret    | fish  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, mouse, lizard, goldfish, horse
The people use 6 different means of transport: bus, roller, snowmobile, scooter, trike, subway
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the lizard and the person driving the bus##2
7. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
9. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet         | pony | turtle | horse      | goldfish | lizard | mouse      |
| Transport   | roller    | subway  | bus | scooter   | trike       | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
There 6 different types of food: grapes, carrot, apricot, cucumber, lime, pear
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, train, van, car, ship, subway
1. the person driving the van is the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person driving the car is the person eating carrot##1
5. the person eating grapes is the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person driving the train is between the person driving the airplane and the person eating pear##2
7. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating pear##1
8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Food        | carrot    | pear | apricot | grapes | lime | cucumber   |
| Transport   | car | ship        | train  | airplane     | subway  | van |

