.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: scientific, fantasy, comedy, time-travel, adventure, romance
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: tennis, sailing, handball, lacrosse, snowboarding, swimming
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific   | time-travel    | romance | comedy | fantasy | adventure   |
| Sport         | snowboarding | tennis | handball | swimming | lacrosse  | sailing |

