.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There 6 different types of food: potato, peas, banana, apricot, cranberry, garlic
The people have 6 different hobbies: drawing, baking, photography, fishing, collecting, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person eating peas##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
5. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is the person eating garlic##1
8. the person eating banana is between the person eating apricot and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
9. the person eating potato is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Food    | potato | garlic | cranberry  | apricot      | banana | peas  |
| Hobby   | baking  | photography    | fishing | drawing | collecting | cooking |

