The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, subway, bus, scooter, airplane, skateboard
1. the person driving the scooter is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the airplane##2
7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
9. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Hobby       | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | magic-tricks | sudoku | dancing |
| Transport   | bus | skateboard    | airplane  | trike    | scooter    | subway    |

