.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  entrepreneur, pilot, analyst, lawyer, software-developer, freelancer
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: pop, folk, country, hip-hop, r&b, dubstep
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of r&b and the fan of pop##2
4. the lawyer is the fan of country##1
5. the analyst is between the pilot and the software-developer##2
6. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
7. the software-developer is on the right of the freelancer##1
8. the software-developer is on the right of the freelancer##1
9. the analyst is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Job           | lawyer | freelancer | software-developer | analyst | pilot | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre   | country   | hip-hop   | folk         | pop    | dubstep     | r&b     |

