.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: reading, drawing, traveling, collecting, writing, baking
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: parkour, weightlifting, water-polo, baseball, tennis, handball
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's sport is handball##2
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | reading   | writing  | drawing | collecting | baking | traveling     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | parkour | handball    | tennis | baseball | water-polo |

