.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: mystery, romance, animation, superhero, martial-arts, adventure
6 different pets are kept: frog, horse, fish, mouse, dog, turtle
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the owner of the horse is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the horse##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching romance movies##2
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the owner of the frog##2
9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | adventure | superhero   | mystery | romance | martial-arts |
| Pet           | frog  | mouse   | fish | horse | turtle       | dog |

