.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
6 different pets are kept: pony, hamster, dog, guinea-pig, bird, rat
The people use 6 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, bike, boat, roller, snowmobile
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 2. the owner of the bird is the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the airplane and the owner of the dog##2
 6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the helicopter##1
 9. the owner of the pony is between the person driving the helicopter and the owner of the hamster##2
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | rat   | bird | dog       | guinea-pig | pony    | hamster |
| Transport   | airplane | roller  | bike | helicopter      | boat | snowmobile        |

