.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, chef, analyst, fisherman, pilot
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: thriller, documentary, drama, western, romance, superhero
 1. the chef is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 3. the mechanic is the person watching western movies##1
 4. the chef is between the analyst and the person watching superhero movies##2
 5. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the fisherman##2
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the architect##1
 7. the mechanic is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the architect##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is the architect##1
10. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Job           | mechanic      | analyst | chef | architect   | pilot  | fisherman |
| Movie-Genre   | western | thriller  | documentary             | superhero | drama | romance       |

