The people prefer 6 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, baseball, weightlifting, handball, tennis
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is handball and the person drinking water##2
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Beverage   | milk   | mirinda   | iced-tea        | water   | almond-milk        | lemonade   |
| Sport      | parkour | handball | weightlifting | baseball | tennis | sailing |

