.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: writing, skydiving, singing, board-games, sudoku, reading
There are 6 different nationalities: egyptian, pakistani, argentine, mexican, american, french
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the mexican is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
 6. the french is on the right of the mexican##1
 7. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the american is on the right of the egyptian##1
 9. the argentine is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is writing##2
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Hobby         | board-games | writing | skydiving | reading | sudoku | singing |
| Nationality   | egyptian | american | argentine      | mexican     | french       | pakistani |

 